Package: oidnChaRts
Type: Package
Title: Utility Functions For htmlwidget Visualisations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Martin", "Hadley", email = "martinjohnhadley@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides templates for creating rich interactive charts/maps/networks, including; bar charts, time series,
    choropleth, scatter geo plots, ego networks and more. All charts are created using htmlwidget libraries, the most widely 
    used libraries are; plotly, highcharter, leaflet and visNetwork. Note that highcharter and other libraries have 
    restrictive licenses - refer to the individual libraries for further information.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
